snippet.title: PlayStation Experience 2015: Psychonauts in the Rhombus of Ruin - Announce Teaser Trailer | PS VR
snippet.description:
Psychonauts in the Rhombus of ruin is a forthcoming PlayStation VR experience by Double Fine Productions,
which takes place immediately after the end of Psychonauts 1, and takes us all the way to the start of
Psychonauts 2.
